-- ฟังก์ชันค้นหา Remote แบบปลอดภัย (ไม่ทำให้สคริปต์ค้าง)
local function getRemotes()
    local events = ReplicatedStorage:FindFirstChild("Events")
    if events then
        return events:FindFirstChild("PlayEmote"), events:FindFirstChild("ModelAnimation")
    end
    return nil, nil
end

local function stopEmote()
    local char = Players.LocalPlayer.Character
    if currentTrack then 
        currentTrack:Stop() 
        currentTrack = nil 
    end

    local _, modelAnimRemote = getRemotes()
    if activeObject and char and modelAnimRemote then
        modelAnimRemote:FireServer(1, activeObject.uuid, activeObject.part, char)
        activeObject = nil
    end
end

local function playEmote()
    stopEmote()

    local emoteName = selectedType .. "Emote" .. selectedNum
    local char = Players.LocalPlayer.Character
    if not char then return end

    local playEmoteRemote, modelAnimRemote = getRemotes()

    if playEmoteRemote then
        playEmoteRemote:FireServer(emoteName)
    end

    local objData = EmoteObjects[emoteName]
    if objData and modelAnimRemote then
        modelAnimRemote:FireServer(0, objData.uuid, objData.part, char)
        activeObject = objData 
    end

    local anim = nil
    for _, v in pairs(game:GetDescendants()) do
        if v.Name == emoteName and v:IsA("Animation") then 
            anim = v 
            break 
        end
    end

    if anim then
        local hum = char:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid")
        if hum then
            currentTrack = hum:LoadAnimation(anim)
            currentTrack.Looped = true
            currentTrack:Play()
        end
    end
end

